metadata.name: Mambhele
metadata.description:
The Xhosa nation (South African origin) is made up of iziduko (clan names). Clans make up tribes and tribes make up nations.

Referring to a person by their clan name is regarded as the highest form of respect.

This here is Mambhele

Bhele, Dlambulo, Khuboni, Langa, Mafu
